surprisingly enough, turning off PC names actually helps a lot too. Hit Shift-n to do it. A guildie told me that when 50+ people were standing at a keep door and I ran a bit smoother after turning it off. I always turn it off in the big cities too.<BR>The only worse than video lag stopping you from casting, are all the Middies with their instants. Quickcast is nothing campared to insta stun/mez.<P>--------------------<P>Daenn Mindspinner<BR>Sorcerer of Albion Palomides<BR>Iron Griffons
